Partitioning for compute nodes:

sda1
	boot 500M
sda2
	vg_computeX
		lv_root 10000 ext4
		lv_swap 6000
		lv_home 4996 ext4
sda3
	vg_gluster 216972
		lv_gluster 215972 xfs



The following are the initial steps that need to be followed prior to running the installation scripts:

yum update -y
yum install -y man nano emacs git
git clone git@github.com:beloglazov/openstack-centos-kvm-glusterfs.git

